Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura... Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Homemade... is probably a bit heavy.\NI've never cooked before, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,On February 14th, I was going\Nto go somewhere with Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and exchange chocolates with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--It'll be exciting to see what Hyodo\Ncan do with their record next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--Anyway, I need to ask her what she likes.\N--It'll be exciting to see what Hyodo\Ncan do with their record next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,--And now, the moment everyone's\Nbeen waiting for, romance horoscopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--I need to make sure I don't regret anything.\N--And now, the moment everyone's\Nbeen waiting for, romance horoscopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shaman Taoka's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...Romance horoscopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Shaman Taoka's Romance Horoscopes"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to tell you all about\Nyour romance luck again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Missed Call Just Now\NTarumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Missed Call Just Now\NTarumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a call when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Libra"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see some rough times ahead\Nfor the Libras today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Libra"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're aware of your surroundings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is... D!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want something? Like milk tea or bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... what's your sign, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. I was born in April...\NOh, April 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she's an Aries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's an Aries, I think our\Ncompatibility sucks, since I'm a Libra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd want to get closer\Nto someone who's not compatible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to know my sign,\Nanyway? Are you into astrology?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I, uh... I need to get\Nready for our next class...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I managed to find out\Nwhen Shimamura's birthday is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tarumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, um... What kind of chocolate do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I think I'm a fan of\Nmilk chocolate. It goes down better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Libra"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam, tap, bam, tap, bam, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Libras...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Change up your hairstyle\Nto really grab your crush's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is A.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna have lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that all chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you, like, use your head too much\Nstudying that you need the extra carbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your ponytail's cute.\NThough I like you just the way you are usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,U-U... Usually?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Your chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Milk chocolate, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Though I like you\Njust the way you are usually."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say how you really feel today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know when you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a lot more positive\Nafter meeting Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm so positive\Nthat I'm about to burst,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but my days are now brighter, nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to tell her\Nhow much I appreciate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura is my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just, um...\Nwanted to talk about the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that part! You wanted to show gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Gratitude, gratitude,\Nhow do I show gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything to\Nget thanked... Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I became\Nmore positive or just stupider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Libras out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure you hurry up and\Ngive them your homemade chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Your lucky letter today is C!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Chocolate They'll Think Is Delicious"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... Chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well?"\N"Well?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I'd feel awkward\Nif someone sent this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Shimamura to be happy.\NI want her to think I'm special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My wishes and desires kept piling up\Nfar and high like mountain ranges,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but what I was seeing before me\Nwas an endless wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was better off before I messed with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tarumi\NIncoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tarumi\NIncoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I didn't call you back earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. We haven't\Ntalked since grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention this the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? Happy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I guess I don't mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at that hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what shocks you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, let's go see a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two go? I've gotta study.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with them. And make sure they get some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let us go!\N--Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I spotted some teacher\Nwith some kids, but it's Shimamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino... Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just got back from some family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Hino. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... Who might you be? Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you've been dragging the runts\Naround today on a family discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to see a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't hang out on our days off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Though maybe I'll go buy some\Nchocolate on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you giving some to Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's more like I'll give it to her\Nand we'll both eat it on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We do that every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... So, why do you buy Nagafuji chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--Why? Because it makes Nagafuji happy?\NAnd we both like chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--Spinny, spin... Spinny, spin...\N--Why? Because it makes Nagafuji happy?\NAnd we both like chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's all there is\Nto a girls' Valentine's together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's way too eager... And she's too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're both overthinking\NValentine's Day way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your destined prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...have an exciting encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna play some games.\NWanna go to Nagafuji's house with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about games, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, I'm not going to twist your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! The gang's all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Chief Adachi: 5,000,000 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Another six. Looks like you're off\Nto a great start, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's my turn... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Pro: 6,500,000 yen"\N"Nippon Budokan"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Pro: 6,500,000 yen"\N"Nippon Budokan"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to keep squishing your boobs. Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Mrs. Hino: 15,000,000 yen"\N"Sunshine 60"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice! Hup...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A one? Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Have some fresh croquettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah! Love you, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is lively today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Hino went off to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuffup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Mrs. Hino: 27,000,000 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do in Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I got Okinawa.\NThe goal is Nagoya, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Dang it, I got a one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Adachicchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only four spaces from the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a four. You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Chief Adachi: 52,000,000 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagoya Castle"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a four.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, the first one in's Adacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. That means I'm in last place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in last place until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Only people with bad personalities\Nare good at this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess you're a great person, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I do think you're a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can play again some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.\N--Be careful getting home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you at least have some fun, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Actually, I think\NI asked you this before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, want me to give you a ride home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be really out of the way. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem way different from when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passes by so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just being trifled with in this\Ncompletely different flow of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, in three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten about the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachi! Eyes up front!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Shimamura is stealing my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But that time, unlike the\Ncolorless days I've spent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is so filled with light, just like a jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... I might not make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly. Or rather, aren't you cold?\NLook at what you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fine adult, so I don't have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An adult, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not showing up to school at that age,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're heading right down the path\Nto becoming a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know, Shimamura,\NI'm around 680 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I actually have school,\Nso see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This ninja art is quite useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja art?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Make Them Turn Around\NBy Staring at Them. {\i1}Nin, nin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja art, my ass. I just came back\Nbecause I'm a really good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, yesh. You sure are\Na good pershon, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I see, thanks"\N"You're not coming today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I see, thanks"\N"Unread: You're not coming today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Unread: You're not coming today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to get closer,\Nyou need to make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep waiting forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I believe your name was Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... So, where's Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So make sure you shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go procure dinner soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I leave this to you, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's Yashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... She said something about procuring dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure does whatever she wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So what brings you here, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, you weren't at school today,\Nso I thought you maybe had a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent you a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I left it in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I came to see how you were doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess I might've woken you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty decent, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When she looks like this,\NI can tell what Adachi wants from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Something she can lean onto that'll support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Previously, it was the gym wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But at some point, that turned into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I don't wonder about why that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fact of the matter is, I am indeed\Nspending time with Adachi like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is A!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This lucky letter was passed down\Nfrom my great ancestor, Himi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait... D-Don't forget to buy chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I need to buy chocolate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Adachi wants to go back to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we insisted on going\Nto that place right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd probably freeze\Nand wouldn't be able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The seasons continue to change,\Nand we go along for the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dandan {\i0}noodles and a\Nhalf order of fried rice up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to call you in suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do though?\NI was planning on buying chocolate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tarumi\NIncoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shima? Sorry to call you out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate... Chocolate...\NChocolate for Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out with Shimamura tomorrow,\Nso I guess I can just pick then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 8 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 8 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 8 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 8 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Fortunetelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see it! I see your future!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.25,0:23:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.25,0:23:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you figured out\Nthat I'm going to kiss you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where does it say that I'm going to kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... The forehead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know about that...
